summary: This is a brief email from an unspecified sender to an unspecified recipient, dated December 30, 2019, attaching a spreadsheet containing IP addresses associated with Ghislaine Maxwell's Facebook logins. It appears to be investigative material related to tracking Maxwell's online activity.

The document indicates active monitoring or investigation of Maxwell's online activity as of late 2019.
